# Project Structure Overview

Top-level
- `app/`: App Router entrypoints, global styles, favicon
- `components/`: Reusable UI (shadcn-style) and feature components
- `lib/`: Utilities
- `public/`: Static assets (images, icons)
- Config: `next.config.ts`, `tsconfig.json`, `eslint.config.mjs`, `postcss.config.mjs`, `components.json`

App directory
- `app/layout.tsx`: Root layout, Inter font, `globals.css`, fixed bottom `Navbar`, metadata
- `app/page.tsx`: Home page rendering `Hero` and `Timeline`
- `app/globals.css`: Tailwind v4 imports, CSS variables (OKLCH), base layer, dark variant
- `app/favicon.ico`: Favicon

Components
- `components/ui/*`: Radix-wrapped primitives (Button, Badge, Avatar, NavigationMenu, Sheet) using `cva` and `cn`
- `components/navbar/*`: `NavMenu` (desktop icons), `NavigationSheet` (mobile), `index.tsx` (container)
- `components/Hero.tsx`: Intro section with avatar, copy, external link badge
- `components/timeline/index.tsx`: Experience timeline with badges and `next/image`
- `components/icons/*`: Custom SVGs (e.g., LinkedIn)

Lib and assets
- `lib/utils.ts`: `cn(...inputs)` wrapper using `clsx` + `tailwind-merge`
- `public/images/*`: Company logos and social icons used by `Timeline`
